prompt:
Patient: Hello?

Nurse: Hi, this is Rachel calling from O'Connor Hospital. I'm an AI on a recorded line. Is this Damian Benton?

Patient: Yeah.

Nurse: Hello Damian, I'm calling on behalf of your primary care doctor, Doctor Marta Marcuso, to check in on you. How have you been doing lately?

Patient: Fine. What do you want?

responses.gpt4: I appreciate you taking this call, Damian. I just wanted to discuss your health and find out how we can maximize your wellness. As part of this conversation, it may add some joy if we also talk about something you enjoy. Is there something you are looking forward to doing this week?
responses.our_model: I'm glad to hear you're doing fine. I'm here to discuss a few topics related to your health. Before we dive into that, is there anything you're looking forward to doing this week?
